			Menu: menuEdit
				Resource Id: 11692
				Title: &Edit
				Description: Simple Edit menu with Undo, Cut, Copy, Paste, Clear.
				Enabled when:
				Status Text: Undo, Cut, Copy, Paste, Clear 
				Menu Item Name:
				Menu Item: &Undo
					Resource Id: 11693
					Menu Item Name:
					Status Text: Reverses the last action
					Keyboard Accelerator: Alt+BkSp
					Menu Settings
						Enabled when: SalEditCanUndo()
						Checked when:
					Menu Actions
						Call SalEditUndo()
				Menu Separator
				Menu Item: Cu&t
					Resource Id: 11694
					Menu Item Name:
